http://www.native-languages.org/crowstory.htm
">Lodge-Boy and Thrown-Away</a>:</b><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
Crow legend about the two mythical brothers Thrown-Behind-The-Curtain and Thrown-In-Spring.
